quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: \"Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere wo…ó…óunde o wonunoo e mun"
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : \"Wata on yeddondir ka Am …óoo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa"
  50,29,Konngol wa…ótitetaake ka Am …óoo ; Mi siforaa kadi too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen
  50,30,"√ëalnde Men wi'anoyta Jahannama on : \"E a heewii?\" Nge wi'a: \"Ko …ìeydee hino woodi"
  50,31,"Aljanna on …ìa…ótinanee gom…óu…ìe …ìen, hara wanaa ka wo…ó…ói"
  50,32,"Ko …óum …óoo woni ko foda…óon, wonannde kala ruttii…óo [e Joomi mun] reenii…óo"
  50,33,"on hulu…óo Jom Hinaranke On ka wirnii, o ardi e …ìernde laa…ìunde"
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam\". Ko nden woni √±alaande luttaynde nden"
  50,35,"Hino woodani …ìe ton kala ko …ìe faaletee, hara kadi …ìeydaari hino ka Amen"
  50,36,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Men halki ado ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìen …ìurnoo…ìe doole, …ìen wanngorii e leydi ndin, ndaarugol taw si …ìe he…ìay laaworde"
  50,37,"Pellet, wonii e …óum, waaju wonannde kala jom …ìernde, maa tu…óu…óo noppi hara ko tawaa…óo"
  50,38,"Gom…óii Men tagii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, nder bal…óe jeegoo, tampere woo he…ìaali Men. @Corrected"
  50,39,"Mu√±√±o e ko …ìe wowlata kon, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa ado pu…óal naange ngen e ado mutal ngal"
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa Mo e ka battane [jul…óe] farlaa…óe"
  50,41,"He…óo, √±alnde noddoowo on noddoyta e nokkuure …ìadiinde"
  50,42,"√±alnde …ìe naniroyta haacaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko nden woni √ëalnnde yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]"
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Menen wuurnata Men wara, ko ka Amen kadi woni ruttorde nden"
  50,44,"√ëalnde leydi ndin seekotoo […ìe yaltira] he√±agol; ko nde woni moo…ìirde newaniinde Men"
  50,45,"Ko Menen …ìuri anndude ko …ìe wowlata kon. A wonaa dooloowo…ìe. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala huloowo kammbaa An on"
  51,1,Mi woondirii keneeli jaroray…ói (leydi) jaragol
  51,2,Mi woondirii duule ronndotoo…óe to…ìo tii…óngo
  51,3,Mi woondirii laa…óe dogiray…óe newaare
  51,4,E peccooji yamiraande
  51,5,"ko podete …óon ko, ko goongo"
  51,6,Haasbeede ko ko wonata
  51,7,Mi woondirii kammu jom …óate ngun
  51,8,"Pellet, hi…óon e konngol luurrangol"
  51,9,Hino yiltee e makko kala firlitaa…óo e gom…óinal
  51,10,Fenoo…ìe …ìen hu…óaama
  51,11,…ìen yollii…ìe e majjere welsindii…ìe
  51,12,"Hi…ìe lamndoo : \"Ko honnde woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe"
  51,13,√ëalaande nde …ìe leptoytee…ìe ka Yiite
  51,14,Mee…óee lepte mon …óen; ko …óum woni ko keppatno…óon kon
  51,15,"Pellet, gom…óu…ìe …ìen wonii e aljannaaji e …ìulli"
  51,16,Jaggatnoo…ìe ko Joom ma…ì…ìe okki…ìe …ìe te ko adii …óuum ko…ìe mo∆¥∆¥inatnoo…ìe
  51,17,Ho…ìe pam…óuno ko…ìe …óaanatoo jemma
  51,18,E saanga ndoogu ho…ìe toro yaafeede
  51,19,Ina e jaw…óe mumen hakke wonande √±aagatoo…ìe e …ìe √±aagataako
  51,20,Ina e nder leydi he maandeeji wonande yananaa…ìe
  51,21,E nder pittaali mon mate on teskataaka
  51,22,Ina e kammu arsuka mon e ko podante …óon
  51,23,E Joom kammu e leydi ko…óum goongo hono no kaalirton nih
  51,24,Mbela arii e maa yeewtere ho…ó…ìe Ibraahiima teddinaa…ìe
  51,25,"Tuma …ìe naatunoo ka makko …ìe wi'i: \"Salaam (Kisiyee mon)\". O maaki: \"Menen ko men …óen∆¥ii …ìe on"
  51,26,O naayii faade e koreeji makko O addori ngaari payndi
  51,27,O …ìadani…ìe ndi o wii on √±aamata
  51,28,"O so*i e mum en kulol, …ìe wii woto hul, …ìe weltiniri…ìe cuklel"
  51,29,"Jom suudu makko ari hombo wulla o hellii yeesa makko, o wii nayeejo dimara"
  51,30,Malaykaaji …ói mbii ko hono nih Joom ma daali ko Kanko woni √±ee√±o Ganndo